{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"When I was five years old"},{"time":4000,"text":"I fell in love with airplanes."},{"time":7000,"text":"Now I'm talking about the '30s."},{"time":10000,"text":"In the '30s an airplane had two wings"},{"time":14000,"text":"and a round motor,"},{"time":17000,"text":"and was always flown"},{"time":19000,"text":"by a guy who looked like Cary Grant."},{"time":23000,"text":"He had high leather boots,"},{"time":26000,"text":"jodhpurs, an old leather jacket,"},{"time":29000,"text":"a wonderful helmet"},{"time":32000,"text":"and those marvelous goggles --"},{"time":34000,"text":"and, inevitably, a white scarf,"},{"time":38000,"text":"to flow in the wind."},{"time":42000,"text":"He'd always walk up to his airplane"},{"time":45000,"text":"in a kind of saunter,"},{"time":48000,"text":"devil-may-care saunter,"},{"time":51000,"text":"flick the cigarette away,"},{"time":54000,"text":"grab the girl waiting here, give her a kiss."},{"time":57000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":58000,"text":"And then mount his airplane,"},{"time":60000,"text":"maybe for the last time."},{"time":62000,"text":"Of course I always wondered what would happen"},{"time":64000,"text":"if he'd kissed the airplane first."},{"time":67000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":75000,"text":"But this was real romance to me."},{"time":78000,"text":"Everything about flying in those years,"},{"time":82000,"text":"which was -- you have to stop and think for a moment --"},{"time":85000,"text":"was probably the most advanced"},{"time":88000,"text":"technological thing going on at the time."},{"time":91000,"text":"So as a youngster,"},{"time":94000,"text":"I tried to get close to this"},{"time":96000,"text":"by drawing airplanes,"},{"time":98000,"text":"constantly drawing airplanes."},{"time":101000,"text":"It's the way I got"},{"time":103000,"text":"a part of this romance."},{"time":105000,"text":"And of course, in a way, when I say romance,"},{"time":108000,"text":"I mean in part"},{"time":110000,"text":"the aesthetics of that whole situation."},{"time":114000,"text":"I think the word is the holistic experience"},{"time":118000,"text":"revolving around a product."},{"time":121000,"text":"The product was that airplane."},{"time":124000,"text":"But it built a romance."},{"time":127000,"text":"Even the parts of the airplane"},{"time":130000,"text":"had French names."},{"time":132000,"text":"Ze fuselage, ze empanage, ze nessal."},{"time":137000,"text":"You know, from a romance language."},{"time":141000,"text":"So that it was something that just got into your spirit."},{"time":144000,"text":"It did mine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":146000,"text":"And I decided I had to get closer than"},{"time":148000,"text":"just drawing fantasy airplanes."},{"time":151000,"text":"I wanted to build airplanes."},{"time":154000,"text":"So I built model airplanes."},{"time":157000,"text":"And I found that in doing the model airplanes"},{"time":163000,"text":"the appearance drawings were not enough."},{"time":166000,"text":"You couldn't transfer those"},{"time":168000,"text":"to the model itself."},{"time":171000,"text":"If you wanted it to fly"},{"time":173000,"text":"you had to learn the discipline"},{"time":176000,"text":"of flying."},{"time":178000,"text":"You had to learn about aeronautics."},{"time":180000,"text":"You had to learn what made an airplane"},{"time":183000,"text":"stay in the air."},{"time":185000,"text":"And of course, as a model in those years, you couldn't control it."},{"time":188000,"text":"So it had to be self-righting,"},{"time":191000,"text":"and stay up without crashing."},{"time":196000,"text":"So I had to give up"},{"time":198000,"text":"the approach of drawing"},{"time":200000,"text":"the fantasy shapes"},{"time":203000,"text":"and convert it to technical drawings --"},{"time":206000,"text":"the shape of the wing, the shape of the fuselage and so on --"},{"time":209000,"text":"and build an airplane over these drawings"},{"time":213000,"text":"that I knew followed some of the principles"},{"time":215000,"text":"of flying."},{"time":217000,"text":"And in so doing, I could produce"},{"time":220000,"text":"a model that would fly, stay in the air."},{"time":223000,"text":"And it had, once it was in the air,"},{"time":226000,"text":"some of this romance that I was in love with."}]},{"cues":[{"time":230000,"text":"Well the act of drawing airplanes"},{"time":233000,"text":"led me to,"},{"time":235000,"text":"when I had the opportunity to choose"},{"time":237000,"text":"a course in school,"},{"time":239000,"text":"led me to sign up for aeronautical engineering."},{"time":243000,"text":"And when I was sitting in classes --"},{"time":247000,"text":"in which no one asked me to draw an airplane --"},{"time":250000,"text":"to my surprise."},{"time":253000,"text":"I had to learn mathematics and mechanics"},{"time":255000,"text":"and all this sort of thing."},{"time":257000,"text":"I'd wile away my time drawing airplanes"},{"time":259000,"text":"in the class."},{"time":261000,"text":"One day a young man looked over my shoulder,"},{"time":264000,"text":"he said, \"You draw very well."},{"time":266000,"text":"You should be in the art department.\""},{"time":269000,"text":"And I said, \"Why?\""},{"time":271000,"text":"And he said, \"Well for one thing, there are more girls there.\""},{"time":274000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":278000,"text":"So my romance was temporarily shifted."},{"time":281000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":282000,"text":"And I went into art"},{"time":284000,"text":"because they appreciated drawing."},{"time":286000,"text":"Studied painting; didn't do very well at that."},{"time":289000,"text":"Went through design,"},{"time":292000,"text":"some architecture."},{"time":294000,"text":"Eventually hired myself out as a designer."},{"time":297000,"text":"And for the following 25 years,"},{"time":300000,"text":"living in Italy,"},{"time":302000,"text":"living in America,"},{"time":304000,"text":"I doled out a piece of this romance"},{"time":308000,"text":"to anybody who'd pay for it --"},{"time":311000,"text":"this sense, this aesthetic feeling,"},{"time":315000,"text":"for the experience revolving around"},{"time":318000,"text":"a designed object."},{"time":321000,"text":"And it exists."},{"time":323000,"text":"Any of you who rode the automobiles --"},{"time":326000,"text":"was it yesterday? --"},{"time":328000,"text":"at the track, you know the romance"},{"time":331000,"text":"revolving around those high performance cars."}]},{"cues":[{"time":337000,"text":"Well in 25 years"},{"time":340000,"text":"I was mostly putting out"},{"time":342000,"text":"pieces of this romance"},{"time":344000,"text":"and not getting a lot back in"},{"time":346000,"text":"because design on call"},{"time":348000,"text":"doesn't always connect you with a circumstance"},{"time":352000,"text":"in which you can produce things of this nature."},{"time":355000,"text":"So after 25 years I began to feel"},{"time":357000,"text":"as though I was running dry."},{"time":360000,"text":"And I quit."},{"time":362000,"text":"And I started up a very small operation --"},{"time":365000,"text":"went from 40 people"},{"time":367000,"text":"to one,"},{"time":369000,"text":"in an effort to rediscover my innocence."},{"time":373000,"text":"I wanted to get back"},{"time":375000,"text":"where the romance was."}]},{"cues":[{"time":378000,"text":"And I couldn't choose airplanes"},{"time":380000,"text":"because they had gotten sort of unromantic"},{"time":383000,"text":"at that point,"},{"time":385000,"text":"even though I'd done a lot of airplane work,"},{"time":387000,"text":"on the interiors."},{"time":389000,"text":"So I chose furniture."},{"time":392000,"text":"And I chose chairs specifically"},{"time":395000,"text":"because I knew something about them."},{"time":397000,"text":"I'd designed a lot of chairs, over the years"},{"time":400000,"text":"for tractors and trucks"},{"time":403000,"text":"and submarines --"},{"time":406000,"text":"all kinds of things."},{"time":408000,"text":"But not office chairs."},{"time":410000,"text":"So I started doing that."},{"time":412000,"text":"And I found that there were ways"},{"time":415000,"text":"to duplicate the same approach"},{"time":418000,"text":"that I used to use on the airplane."},{"time":421000,"text":"Only this time,"},{"time":423000,"text":"instead of the product being shaped by the wind,"},{"time":426000,"text":"it was shaped by the human body."},{"time":430000,"text":"So the discipline was --"},{"time":432000,"text":"as in the airplane you learn a lot about"},{"time":434000,"text":"how to deal with the air,"},{"time":437000,"text":"for a chair"},{"time":439000,"text":"you have to learn a lot about how to deal"},{"time":441000,"text":"with the body,"},{"time":443000,"text":"and what the body needs, wants,"},{"time":445000,"text":"indicates it needs."},{"time":448000,"text":"And that's the way, ultimately"},{"time":450000,"text":"after some ups and downs,"},{"time":454000,"text":"I ended up designing the chair I'm going to show you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":457000,"text":"I should say one more thing. When I was doing those"},{"time":461000,"text":"model airplanes,"},{"time":463000,"text":"I did everything."},{"time":465000,"text":"I conceived the kind of airplane."},{"time":468000,"text":"I basically engineered it."},{"time":471000,"text":"I built it."},{"time":473000,"text":"And I flew it."},{"time":475000,"text":"And that's the way I work now."},{"time":482000,"text":"When I started this chair"},{"time":484000,"text":"it was not a preconceived notion."},{"time":487000,"text":"Design nowadays, if you mean it,"},{"time":490000,"text":"you don't start with styling sketches."},{"time":494000,"text":"I started with a lot of loose ideas,"},{"time":497000,"text":"roughly eight or nine years ago."},{"time":500000,"text":"And the loose ideas had something"},{"time":503000,"text":"to do with what I knew happened with"},{"time":505000,"text":"people in the office,"},{"time":507000,"text":"at the work place -- people who worked,"},{"time":509000,"text":"and used task seating,"},{"time":512000,"text":"a great many of them sitting in front of a computer"},{"time":515000,"text":"all day long."},{"time":517000,"text":"And I felt,"},{"time":519000,"text":"the one thing they don't need,"},{"time":521000,"text":"is a chair that interferes"},{"time":523000,"text":"with their main reason for sitting there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":526000,"text":"So I took the approach"},{"time":529000,"text":"that the chair should do as much for them"},{"time":532000,"text":"as humanly possible"},{"time":534000,"text":"or as mechanistically possible"},{"time":538000,"text":"so that they didn't have to fuss with it."},{"time":540000,"text":"So my idea was that,"},{"time":542000,"text":"instead of sitting down and reaching"},{"time":544000,"text":"for a lot of controls,"},{"time":546000,"text":"that you would sit on the chair,"},{"time":548000,"text":"and it would automatically balance your weight"},{"time":551000,"text":"against the force required"},{"time":554000,"text":"to recline."},{"time":556000,"text":"Now that may not mean a lot to some of you."},{"time":559000,"text":"But you know most good chairs do recline"},{"time":562000,"text":"because it's beneficial to open up this joint"},{"time":565000,"text":"between your legs and your upper body"},{"time":567000,"text":"for better breathing"},{"time":569000,"text":"and better flow."},{"time":571000,"text":"So that if you sit down"},{"time":574000,"text":"on my chair,"},{"time":576000,"text":"whether you're five feet tall"},{"time":578000,"text":"or six foot six,"},{"time":580000,"text":"it always deals with your weight"},{"time":584000,"text":"and transfers the amount of force required"},{"time":588000,"text":"to recline"},{"time":590000,"text":"in a way that you don't have to look"},{"time":593000,"text":"for something to adjust."}]},{"cues":[{"time":595000,"text":"I'll tell you right up front,"},{"time":597000,"text":"this is a trade off."},{"time":599000,"text":"There are drawbacks to this."},{"time":602000,"text":"One is: you can't"},{"time":604000,"text":"accommodate everybody."},{"time":606000,"text":"There are some very light people,"},{"time":609000,"text":"some extremely heavy people,"},{"time":611000,"text":"maybe people with a lot of bulk up top."},{"time":614000,"text":"They begin to fall off the end of your chart."},{"time":617000,"text":"But the compromise, I felt,"},{"time":619000,"text":"was in my favor"},{"time":621000,"text":"because most people don't adjust their chairs."},{"time":624000,"text":"They will sit in them forever."},{"time":626000,"text":"I had somebody on the bus out to the racetrack"},{"time":629000,"text":"tell me about his sister calling him."},{"time":631000,"text":"He said she had one of the new, better chairs."},{"time":634000,"text":"She said, \"Oh I love it.\""},{"time":636000,"text":"She said, \"But it's too high.\""},{"time":638000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":641000,"text":"So he said, \"Well I'll come over and look at it.\""},{"time":644000,"text":"He came over and looked at it."},{"time":646000,"text":"He reached down. He pulled a lever. And the chair sank down."},{"time":650000,"text":"She said, \"Oh it's wonderful. How did you do that?\""},{"time":652000,"text":"And he showed her the lever."},{"time":654000,"text":"Well, that's typical"},{"time":656000,"text":"of a lot of us working in chairs."},{"time":658000,"text":"And why should you"},{"time":660000,"text":"get a 20-page manual"},{"time":662000,"text":"about how to run a chair?"},{"time":664000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":666000,"text":"I had one for a wristwatch once. 20 pages."}]},{"cues":[{"time":670000,"text":"Anyway, I felt that it was important"},{"time":672000,"text":"that you didn't have to make an adjustment"},{"time":675000,"text":"in order to get this kind of action."},{"time":678000,"text":"The other thing I felt was that armrests"},{"time":680000,"text":"had never really been properly approached"},{"time":685000,"text":"from the standpoint of how much"},{"time":688000,"text":"of an aid they could be"},{"time":690000,"text":"to your work life."},{"time":692000,"text":"But I felt it was too much to ask"},{"time":695000,"text":"to have to adjust each individual armrest"},{"time":697000,"text":"in order to get it where you wanted."},{"time":700000,"text":"So I spent a long time."},{"time":702000,"text":"I said I worked eight or nine years on it."},{"time":705000,"text":"And each of these things went along"},{"time":707000,"text":"sort of in parallel"},{"time":709000,"text":"but incrementally were a problem of their own."},{"time":712000,"text":"I worked a long time on figuring out"},{"time":714000,"text":"how to move the arms over a much greater arc --"},{"time":719000,"text":"that is up and down --"},{"time":721000,"text":"and make them a lot easier,"},{"time":724000,"text":"so that you didn't have to use a button."},{"time":727000,"text":"And so after many trials, many failures,"},{"time":729000,"text":"we came up with a very simple arrangement"},{"time":732000,"text":"in which we could just move"},{"time":734000,"text":"one arm or the other."},{"time":736000,"text":"And they go up easily."},{"time":738000,"text":"And stop where you want."},{"time":741000,"text":"You can put them down, essentially out of the way."},{"time":744000,"text":"No arms at all."},{"time":746000,"text":"Or you can pull them up where you want them."},{"time":749000,"text":"And this was another thing that I felt,"},{"time":751000,"text":"while not nearly as romantic"},{"time":754000,"text":"as Cary Grant,"},{"time":756000,"text":"nevertheless begins to"},{"time":759000,"text":"grab a little bit of aesthetic"},{"time":762000,"text":"operation, aesthetic performance"},{"time":765000,"text":"into a product."}]},{"cues":[{"time":767000,"text":"The next area that was of interest to me"},{"time":770000,"text":"was the fact that reclining"},{"time":773000,"text":"was a very important factor."},{"time":775000,"text":"And the more you can recline,"},{"time":777000,"text":"in a way, the better it is."},{"time":780000,"text":"The more the angle between here and here opens up --"},{"time":783000,"text":"and nowadays, with a screen in front of you,"},{"time":786000,"text":"you don't want to have your eye drop too far in the recline,"},{"time":789000,"text":"so we keep it at more or less the same level --"},{"time":793000,"text":"but you transfer weight"},{"time":796000,"text":"off your tailbones."},{"time":798000,"text":"Would everybody put their hand under their bottom"},{"time":801000,"text":"and feel their tailbone?"},{"time":803000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":805000,"text":"You feel that bone under there?"},{"time":807000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":808000,"text":"Just your own."},{"time":810000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":816000,"text":"There's two of them, one on either side."},{"time":821000,"text":"All the weight of your upper torso --"},{"time":823000,"text":"your arms, your head --"},{"time":825000,"text":"goes right down through your back,"},{"time":828000,"text":"your spine, into those bones when you sit."},{"time":832000,"text":"And that's a lot of load."},{"time":834000,"text":"Just relieving your arms with armrests"},{"time":836000,"text":"takes 20 percent of that load off."},{"time":839000,"text":"Now that, if your spine is not held in a good position,"},{"time":844000,"text":"will help bend your spine the wrong way, and so on."},{"time":849000,"text":"So to unload"},{"time":851000,"text":"that great weight --"},{"time":855000,"text":"if that indeed exists --"},{"time":857000,"text":"you can recline."},{"time":860000,"text":"When you recline you take away a lot of that load"},{"time":863000,"text":"off your bottom end, and transfer it to your back."},{"time":866000,"text":"At the same time, as I say, you open up this joint."},{"time":869000,"text":"And breathability is good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":872000,"text":"But to do that, if you have any"},{"time":876000,"text":"amount of recline,"},{"time":880000,"text":"it gets to the point where you need a headrest"},{"time":883000,"text":"because nearly always,"},{"time":887000,"text":"automatically hold your head"},{"time":889000,"text":"in a vertical position, see?"},{"time":891000,"text":"As I recline, my head says more or less vertical."},{"time":896000,"text":"Well if you're reclined a great deal,"},{"time":898000,"text":"you have to use muscle force"},{"time":900000,"text":"to hold your head there."},{"time":902000,"text":"So that's where a headrest comes in."},{"time":904000,"text":"Now headrest is a challenge"},{"time":906000,"text":"because you want it to adjust"},{"time":909000,"text":"enough so that it'll fit,"},{"time":913000,"text":"you know, a tall guy and a short girl."},{"time":916000,"text":"So here we are."},{"time":918000,"text":"I've got five inches of adjustment here"},{"time":922000,"text":"in order to get the headrest in the right place."},{"time":925000,"text":"But then I knew from experience"},{"time":927000,"text":"and looking around in offices"},{"time":930000,"text":"where there were chairs with headrests"},{"time":933000,"text":"that nobody would ever bother"},{"time":935000,"text":"to reach back and turn a knob"},{"time":938000,"text":"and adjust the headrest to put it in position."},{"time":940000,"text":"And you need it in a different position"},{"time":942000,"text":"when you're upright, then when you're reclined."},{"time":944000,"text":"So I knew that had to be solved, and had to be automatic."},{"time":948000,"text":"So if you watch this chair"},{"time":950000,"text":"as I recline, the headrest comes up"},{"time":953000,"text":"to meet my neck."},{"time":955000,"text":"Ideally you want to put the head support"},{"time":959000,"text":"in the cranial area, right there."},{"time":963000,"text":"So that part of it took a long time"},{"time":968000,"text":"to work out."}]},{"cues":[{"time":970000,"text":"And there is a variety of other things: the shape of the cushions,"},{"time":973000,"text":"the gel we put."},{"time":976000,"text":"We stole the idea from bicycle seats,"},{"time":979000,"text":"and put gel in the cushions"},{"time":981000,"text":"and in the armrests"},{"time":983000,"text":"to absorb point load --"},{"time":987000,"text":"distributes the loading so you don't get hard spots."},{"time":990000,"text":"You cant hit your elbow"},{"time":992000,"text":"on bottom."},{"time":994000,"text":"And I did want to demonstrate"},{"time":997000,"text":"the fact that the chair can accommodate people."},{"time":1002000,"text":"While you're sitting in it you can adjust it"},{"time":1004000,"text":"down for the five-footer,"},{"time":1007000,"text":"or you can adjust it"},{"time":1010000,"text":"for the six-foot-six guy --"},{"time":1015000,"text":"all within the scope of a few simple adjustments."},{"time":1021000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}